  "title": "Accounts Payable Officer (Up to $4500) #NKA",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: </strong>Pasir Panjang<br /></p><p><strong>Duration: </strong>6 months contract<br /></p><p><strong>Working Hours: </strong>8:30am - 5pm (Mon - Thurs), 8:30am - 4pm (Friday)<br /></p><p><strong>Salary: </strong>Up to $4500<br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Process and verify supplier invoices and payment requests</li><li><p>Prepare payments and ensure timely disbursement</p></li><li><p>Handle vendor enquiries and resolve discrepancies</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate AP records and documentation</p></li><li><p>Assist with month-end closing and reconciliations</p></li><li><p>Support audits and ad-hoc finance duties</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma or Degree in Accounting, Finance, or related field with 1 year of AP experience</li><li><p>Familiar with accounting systems and strong Excel skills.</p></li></ul><p><br />Ally<br />The Outsourcing Team<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />EA: 99C4599</p>",
